<h2>What is a <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Virtual_private_network" target="blank">VPN</a></h2>

<p>
   It is a virtual private network.  It creates a secure (encrypted) channel between your computer and
   the VPN server.  This prevents people and organizations from spying on what you are doing online.
   It can also help hide the source of the person doing the web browsing.  
</p>


